nodes.name: There's Whiskey
nodes.description: What’s in your bar cart? Please tell us; There’s whiskey always available! A bottle for every taste, made in every corner of the world, specific to your identity.

nodes.name: Vino Sipping
nodes.description: Oh yes, let us pour ourselves a glass. It’s now after hours, and what are you drinking; a white, red, rosé, sparkling, or a fortified wine?

nodes.name: We Wanderlust
nodes.description: The desire to travel has taken on a new meaning. We wanderlust with our sights on the next journey. Where do you wish to create new memories?

nodes.name: Stargazing
nodes.description: The beauty of after the sun sets is the opportunity to look up at the stars. As we gaze up at these most recognized astronomical objects, we also look into a galaxy.

nodes.name: Bra Free Zone
nodes.description: No bras are needed here for your relaxation. Let's ditch the bra to promote breast cancer awareness and gender equality; the present is female.

nodes.name: Weekend Brunching
nodes.description: Now, this is an extreme sport only for the brave and sultry. We know the best bottomless brunches are created with good company.

nodes.name: I Got Your Back
nodes.description: Who doesn't enjoy a massage?! Our massage candle is formulated to burn at a lower and safe temperature for usage. This product is also made with soy wax, vegetable-based, and enriched with all-natural butter and oils. Time to relax, ignite the candle for 25-35 minutes, let the candle melt a pool, put out, and let it set before usage. Massage sold separately.

nodes.name: With My Tribe
nodes.description: They understand you, they resonate with you, and they share similar values and beliefs. They are your soul tribe.

nodes.name: Here We Gather
nodes.description: Where there is light, there is joy in gathering. We know you will find the perfect space for a candle that brings us together to unwind after the sun sets.

nodes.name: Big Thinking
nodes.description: Now I know we don't want to say we think small, but are you tapping into how you can play a significant role and show up bigger in life? Well, now that's big thinking.

nodes.name: Goal Digging
nodes.description: Read it again; Goal Digging is definitely goals! Set often, adjust, short and long term, and make them SMART. Last but not least, obtained goals come with rewards!

nodes.name: Discover
nodes.description: Be the first to find the perfect Discovery tool to unlocking your quintessential scent. This Discovery Set will let you discover your top 3 scents out of our eight staple collection scents. Let your nose do the work.

nodes.name: Don't Bug Me
nodes.description: Don't let those mosquitos bug you! This outdoor living candle is great for your backyard, patio, terrace, or balcony. Get back to enjoying an outdoor evening with new candlelight.
